title: Cezanne Exhibition Poster
description:
Poster developed from Paul Cezanne’s Bathers (Les Grandes Baigneuses), About 1894 - 1905.

This exhibition is the first major retrospective of the Cezanne’s work in the United States in more than 25 years and the first exhibition on Cezanne organized by the Art Institute of Chicago in more than 70 years. This groundbreaking retrospective sheds new light not only on how this pivotal artist created his works, but also why his art remains so vital today. 

  • Dimensions:  24 x 27 in.
  • Material: Premium Cardstock.
